arts.ttl: Heerenveen too strong for Willem II
arts.sum: Heerenveen boosted their chances of a European playoff spot with a 3-1 win over Willem II. The home side started brightly and after two missed chances, Ion Nicolaescu made it 1-0 with a good finish from a Luuk Brouwers cross.
